               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This accession consists of John William Sterling's personal and family correspondence; legal documents; certificates; account book, 1843-1869; writings; speeches; biographical information; and photographs, including portraits of Sterling and other members of the Yale College Class of 1864, and a group photograph of Skull and Bones featuring Sterling.</p>
            </scopecontent>
